rdf:Description.machine:description: A minimalist, line-art illustration of a coffee bag, prominently featuring a coffee bean icon in the center. The design is rendered in a warm, earthy brown color, evoking a sense of natural and organic quality. The clean lines and simple style make it ideal for modern, eco-friendly branding campaigns.
rdf:Description.machine:shortdescription: Minimalist line-art coffee bag illustration with a coffee bean icon in earthy brown color.
